{
  "id": "adv_card_mna_05_03",
  "title": "長瀬麻奈 3話 笑顔で頑張って！",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "sfx",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cheers-in-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――大晦日　番組本番直前",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――New Year's Eve‚ right before the show",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_05_03/sud_vo_adv_cmn_mna_glad-10.m4a",
      "text": "凄いね、こんなに人が集まってる……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Wow‚ so many people are gathered here…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 2.6666667144,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "ステージの前も！　上も！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "In front of the stage! And above!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 5.7384498194,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 8.2333333176
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_05_03-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "さすがにいつもの現場とは雰囲気が違うな……\n超大御所演歌歌手の人が、すぐそこに……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "This atmosphere is way different from our usual gigs…\nThat super famous enka singer is right over there…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 12.4999999842,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 16.7333333176
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_05_03/sud_vo_adv_cmn_mna_yes-13.m4a",
      "text": "リハとは全然熱気も違うね……大舞台だよ、どうする？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The energy is totally different from rehearsals… It’s a big stage‚ what are you gonna do?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 16.7333333176,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_05_03-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "どうするも何も……俺は信じて送り出すだけだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What am I gonna do? …There's nothing for me to do but believe in you and send you off.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 22.2333314103,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 26.7999980769
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_05_03/sud_vo_adv_cmn_mna_surp-06.m4a",
      "text": "えぇ～！？　一緒に大舞台に立つんでしょ！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Huh~!? We're standing on a big stage together‚ aren't we!?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 26.7999980769,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_05_03/sud_vo_adv_cmn_mna_angry-04.m4a",
      "text": "緊張しないの！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Aren't you nervous!?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 29.8821174267,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 31.800003799
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_05_03-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "いや、舞台に立つのは麻奈だけだから\n……でも、うーん、そうだな。一緒にか……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No‚ you're the only one standing on the stage.\n…But‚ hmm‚ you're right. Let's stand on the st…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 35.4333371324,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_05_03/sud_vo_adv_cmn_mna_hey-01.m4a",
      "text": "大舞台を前に、今どんなお気持ちですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "How are you feeling right now‚ standing before such a grand stage?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 40.8333371324,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_05_03/sud_vo_adv_cmn_mna_yes-06.m4a",
      "text": "はいっ、{user}くん、答えて！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Okay‚ {user}‚ answer!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 44.514216275,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 47.4333317918
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_05_03/sud_vo_adv_cmn_mna_glad-12.m4a",
      "text": "私もインタビュアー、やってみたかったんだよねー",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I wanted to try being an interviewer too~.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 47.4333317918,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 51.4666646166
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_05_03-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "……そうだな。これまで一緒に頑張ってきた分は\n麻奈がステージに連れて行ってくれる",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Well‚ I know that all the effort we've put in together\nwill lead to Mana taking us to that stage‚ Mana.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 55.4666646166,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_05_03-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "それが分かっているので、なんの不安もありません",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So I have no worries at all.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 58.2999979499,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 62.1333312832
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "……{user}くん……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…{user}…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 62.1333312832,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_05_03/sud_vo_adv_cmn_mna_glad-05.m4a",
      "text": "そうだよね。今日まで一緒に積み重ねてきたもんね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That’s right. We’ve built up to this together.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 64.7043154969,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_05_03-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "い、いや、その\n頑張ったのはもちろん麻奈だからな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "N-no‚ that’s not…\nOf course you’re the one who worked hard‚ Mana.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 71.2333206021,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 74.0333206021
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "でも、頑張れたのは",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But I was able to work hard",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 74.0333206021,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_05_03/sud_vo_adv_cmn_mna_glad-01.m4a",
      "text": "{user}くんのおかげだから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Because of you‚ {user}.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 76.5276318156,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_05_03/sud_vo_adv_cmn_mna_enter-03.m4a",
      "text": "……そろそろ、行ってくるね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…It’s about time… I’m heading out.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 79.0333206021,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_05_03-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "あぁ。頑張ってこい！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah. Go get ‘em!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 81.9666549527,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_festivalstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "festivalstage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 86.0833251798
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_05_03/sud_vo_adv_cmn_mna_mananame-02.m4a",
      "text": "みんな！　長瀬麻奈です！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Everyone! It’s Nagase Mana!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 87.1333251798,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_05_03/sud_vo_adv_cmn_mna_laughter-09.m4a",
      "text": "一年の最後、大晦日に一緒に過ごせるなんて",
      "translations": {
        "en": "To think we can spend the last day of the year‚ New Year’s Eve‚ together…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 89.8999954068,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_05_03/sud_vo_adv_cmn_mna_glad-09.m4a",
      "text": "本当に嬉しい！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’m so happy!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 93.381349873,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_05_03/sud_vo_adv_cmn_mna_glad-02.m4a",
      "text": "昔から観ていた舞台に立てて、夢みたい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It’s like a dream to be standing on a stage I’ve been watching since I was little.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 95.7666717373,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "これも、みんなが応援してくれたおかげだよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It’s all thanks to your support.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 99.0489672153,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cheers-in-01.m4a",
          "delay": 8417.704919100004,
          "startTime": 107.4666721344
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "いつも本当にありがとう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Thank you so much‚ always.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 102.466676315,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_05_03/sud_vo_adv_cmn_mna_fan-07.m4a",
      "text": "今年最後の元気を、みんなに贈ります！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’m giving you all my last bit of energy for this year!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 104.5954110023,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_05_03-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "（大舞台でも、あいつは変わらないな）\n（……こちらこそ、いつもありがとう、麻奈）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Even on a big stage‚ she doesn’t change‚ huh.）\n（…Thank you‚ too‚ Mana‚ always.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 112.700010157,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_festivalstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "festivalstage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 117.8703216397
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
